      "content": "that's a great start, really sets the mood. i want to zoom in on the people a bit more to make it feel more real. can you describe some of the characters or groups you might see hanging out on these corners or in these alleys? like, what do they look like, what are they wearing, and what's the vibe they give off to someone just passing through? i need that sense of immediate threat or unease.",
